  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you reach 14th level, you can magically open temporary conduits to watery destinations. As an action, you can <strong>teleport </strong>yourself and up to five other willing creatures that you can see within 30 feet of you. Amid a whirl of tentacles, you all vanish and then reappear up to 1 mile away in a body of water you've seen (pond size or larger) or within 30 feet of it, each of you appearing in an unoccupied space within 30 feet of the others.</p>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a <strong>short</strong> or <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
